wnloadContentCatalog.java", "mobile/android/base/moz.build", "mobile/android/tests/background/junit4/src/org/mozilla/gecko/dlc/catalog/TestDownloadContentCatalog.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "18cde0ee42b5e719d553e06dedadcb5254b59879", "parents": ["fc43fe3b9c06af6346860a85e9c340c606951338"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Evan Tseng \u003cevan@tseng.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1386560 - Fix the typo of firefoxAccountCategory header's class list because all level 1 headers should have the subcategory class. r=jaws, a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 8ngQaCWSUxq", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/in-content-new/sync.xul"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e03569e878c08a1f5b687c26f25650d450bff5d6", "parents": ["18cde0ee42b5e719d553e06dedadcb5254b59879"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tomislav Jovanovic \u003ctomica@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1385864 - Drop invalid optional_permissions from manifests. r=kmag, a=lizzard\n\nCLOSED TREE\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Df2wjNOTVkF", "files": ["toolkit/components/extensions/schemas/manifest.json", "toolkit/components/extensions/test/xpcshell/test_ext_unknown_permissions.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "739ff1fa9eafa651477370059747ab3e80bbfd74", "parents": ["e03569e878c08a1f5b687c26f25650d450bff5d6"], "tags": []}], "date": 1501940286, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "7576": {"changesets": [{"author": "Grigory Kruglov \u003cgkruglov@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1275423 - Update failing DSA signature tests. r=nalexander, a=test-only on a CLOSED TREE\n\n- use EOJ's handy .equals() to compare JSON structures\n- generated DSA signature prefix seem to have changed post Java 1.8 update\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: JwQLb998Kro", "files": ["mobile/android/tests/background/junit4/src/org/mozilla/gecko/browserid/test/TestJSONWebTokenUtils.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "706a35d8549e9abc807580e031fc15d1f28c3967", "parents": ["739ff1fa9eafa651477370059747ab3e80bbfd74"], "tags": []}], "date": 1501940527, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "7577": {"changesets": [{"author": "tbirdbld", "branch": "THUNDERBIRD560b1_2017080511_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Automated checkin: version bump for thunderbird 56.0b1 release. DONTBUILD CLOSED TREE a=release", "files": [], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "780eb39b667ae5c468e408fa47923b382390f2dd", "parents": ["74e49a52007c609495c6cbc673487ed457838d9e"], "tags": ["THUNDERBIRD_56_0b1_BUILD2", "THUNDERBIRD_56_0b1_RELEASE"]}, {"author": "tbirdbld", "branch": "THUNDERBIRD560b1_2017080511_RELBRANCH", "desc": "Added THUNDERBIRD_56_0b1_RELEASE THUNDERBIRD_56_0b1_BUILD2 tag(s) for changeset 780eb39b667a. DONTBUILD CLOSED TREE a=release", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "06a3f28d08b5ddb46f7b5f21c6560e4b839abe38", "parents": ["780eb39b667ae5c468e408fa47923b382390f2dd"], "tags": []}], "date": 1501947406, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "tbirdbld"}, "7578": {"changesets": [{"author": "Cameron McCormack \u003ccam@mcc.id.au\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1381731 - Remove gUnusedAtomCount assertions since they're hard to get right given OMT atom refcounting. r=bholley, a=NPOTB\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: ByM6mzL1IgF", "files": ["xpcom/ds/nsAtomTable.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bf61f9884b5b3b22b5c7d9606cffb5ebffd70be4", "parents": ["706a35d8549e9abc807580e031fc15d1f28c3967"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Justin Wood \u003cCallek@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387532 - Beta is scheduling multiple Win8 opt reftest-noaccel runs on every push. r=catlee, a=test-only\n\nThe issue here is that we had marked 'chunked' as false, but were still trying to use 8 chunks for reftest. Because of this we were also sending the unchunked buildbot name to BBB for each chunk we actually tried to run, on e10s and other variants.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 3Ffv8UMBzk2", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/test/tests.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c342cab423f6de346ac5c2daeeceebc715b5f84c", "parents": ["bf61f9884b5b3b22b5c7d9606cffb5ebffd70be4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Justin Wood \u003cCallek@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387532 - Enforce that we don't schedule multiple chunks for the same test without passing buildbot the required chunking information. r=catlee, a=test-only\n\nThe issue here is that we had marked 'chunked' as false, but were still trying to use 8 chunks for reftest. Because of this we were also sending the unchunked buildbot name to BBB for each chunk we actually tried to run, on e10s and other variants.\n\nCLOSED TREE\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Dc5npIq5sxr", "files": ["taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/mozharness_test.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "08ab8a747932d8a65e8940269cd1ea4aea907a0e", "parents": ["c342cab423f6de346ac5c2daeeceebc715b5f84c"], "tags": []}], "date": 1501948235, "git_changesets": [null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "7579": {"changesets": [{"author": "Justin Wood \u003cCallek@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387867 - Disable gtest on windows devedition, it is permafailing because we PGO these builds. r=jlorenzo, a=test-only\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: E2UyYfjbAmj", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/test/tests.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c4497cbdc4677a0857282c01bbf23bfbb7d82a16", "parents": ["08ab8a747932d8a65e8940269cd1ea4aea907a0e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Alexandre Poirot \u003cpoirot.alex@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1078284 - Disable WebIDE tests on all but optimized builds. r=jryans, a=test-only\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 7ORmJaJIrtD", "files": ["devtools/client/webide/test/browser.ini", "devtools/client/webide/test/chrome.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "df856413bbfbf5b81ea957d85a8982e8e85b81c7", "parents": ["c4497cbdc4677a0857282c01bbf23bfbb7d82a16"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ben Kelly \u003cben@wanderview.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387211 - Avoid potential deadlock during worker shutdown. r=billm, a=lizzard", "files": ["dom/workers/WorkerPrivate.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cbed0550193a54f676d96fb540a0d9d40023e526", "parents": ["df856413bbfbf5b81ea957d85a8982e8e85b81c7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tooru Fujisawa \u003carai_a@mac.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1385112 - Use uint32_t in TokenStream::skipChars. r=anba, a=lizzard", "files": ["js/src/frontend/TokenStream.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c743648bf55b896d1721a86b635e2d007b4accd8", "parents": ["cbed0550193a54f676d96fb540a0d9d40023e526"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Munro Mengjue Chiang \u003cmchiang@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1386974 - Set the preference for android hardware encoder to true in default. r=jib, a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1J9TuYhxevF", "files": ["modules/libpref/init/all.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c5ae0367e5f0bd92f4dfbdf93eb26bd75144c911", "parents": ["c743648bf55b896d1721a86b635e2d007b4accd8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Doug Thayer \u003cdothayer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1385396 - Cache early setExperimentActive calls. r=gfritzsche, a=lizzard\n\nCalling setExperimentActive too early during startup can change\nthe order of some initialization. setExperimentActive probably\nshouldn't have this kind of effect, so simply cache early calls\nto it until gGlobalEnvironment has been initialized through other\nfunctions.\n\nAdditionally, I am speculatively including work to ensure that\nsetExperimentInactive and getActiveExperiments have the same\nbehavior, while remaining correct by working from the same cache\nthat setExperimentActive uses.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: IlzT1J0o6gK", "files": ["toolkit/components/telemetry/TelemetryEnvironment.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ea9b41d34bde51311f9bc140b808249a1040d2ed", "parents": ["c5ae0367e5f0bd92f4dfbdf93eb26bd75144c911"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Blake Kaplan \u003cmrbkap@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387626 - Move to 100% of eligible users on beta. r=Felipe, a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: EkVvGAZfZJI", "files": ["browser/extensions/e10srollout/bootstrap.js", "browser/extensions/e10srollout/install.rdf.in"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ed2236574f7e9ba7867dd0fed74412e09a8bf19e", "parents": ["ea9b41d34bde51311f9bc140b808249a1040d2ed"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Landry Breuil \u003clandry@openbsd.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387510 - Use glob() when looking for libclang.so on OpenBSD. r=froydnj, a=lizzard", "files": ["toolkit/moz.configure"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "30c7a38928b122be34c555c8a2354c1846f0bb21", "parents": ["ed2236574f7e9ba7867dd0fed74412e09a8bf19e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Alastor Wu \u003calwu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387917 - Turn on the pref media.block-autoplay-until-in-foreground by default. r=bwu, a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 7KNLYSeSXDu", "files": ["modules/libpref/init/all.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "524c06e940a4688ef58c2542d430ca03fe842bdc", "parents": ["30c7a38928b122be34c555c8a2354c1846f0bb21"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1382568 - Avoid trying to resolve styles in an uninitialized presshell in GetInnerText. r=heycam, a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: DFFb5OCQpHG", "files": ["dom/html/nsGenericHTMLElement.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f5864cfeab489250412e0210a7d4724a309f4a6f", "parents": ["524c06e940a4688ef58c2542d430ca03fe842bdc"], "ta